column5: I came across this and thought ...OFC has members everywhere so ...here ya go...lets hope for a happy ending
I'm hoping for a happy ending  also.  Please keep us posted.
I thought they found her days ago
Yes, thankfully she was found around 8:30 Monday morning by a SAR helicopter.
OPP sure is getting good use out of their new choppers!  Glad they found her!
wonderful news...sorry i didnt realize she was found...thanks for updating
